import jax.numpy as jnp
import jax.random as jrd


import pandas as pd

import sdg4varselect.plotting as sdgplt
from joint_model import algo_factory

from joint_model import PolyMixedEffectsModel, p_mem_names
from joint_model import MixtureCoxModel, p_surival_names
from joint_model import WeibullCoxMemJointModel, p_jm_names
from joint_model import plot_T_hist_weibull, plot_digestibility
from time import time

sdgplt.FIGSIZE = 8
key = int(time())
jax_key = jrd.PRNGKey(key)

mode = "plotting"
mode = "estimation"
mode = "jm and mem"
mode = "only_jm"
mode = "only_sm"
mode = "plotting"

# =========================
# 3. Load and Prepare Digestibility Data
# =========================
data_dig_obs = pd.read_csv("digestibilite_py.csv", sep=";", index_col=0, decimal=",")
data_dig_obs = data_dig_obs.rename(
    {"sampling.diff.TT.flo": "sampling_obs"}, axis="columns"
)
data_dig_obs = data_dig_obs.sort_values(by=["id_geno_semis", "sampling_obs"])
dig_id = jnp.array(data_dig_obs["id_geno_semis"])
data_dig_obs.head()

# =========================
# 4. Load and Prepare Flowering Data
# =========================
data_flowering = pd.read_csv("flowering_py.csv", sep=";", index_col=0, decimal=",")
data_flowering = data_flowering.sort_values(by=["id_geno_semis"])
data_flowering.head()

shape = (data_dig_obs.shape[0] // 12, 8 + 4)
data = {
    "mem_obs_time": jnp.array(data_dig_obs["sampling_obs"]).reshape(shape),
    "mem_obs_time_date": jnp.array(data_dig_obs["sampling.date"]).reshape(shape),
    "Y": jnp.array(data_dig_obs.digestibilite).reshape(shape),
    "sowing": jnp.array([data_flowering[f"S{i}"] for i in [1, 2]], dtype=jnp.int16).T,
    "P": jnp.array(data_flowering["precocite"]),
}

# =========================
# 5. Load and Prepare Pest Data
# =========================
data_pest_obs = pd.read_csv("pest_py.csv", sep=";", index_col=0, decimal=",")
data_pest_obs = data_pest_obs.sort_values(by="id_geno_semis")
pest_id = jnp.array(data_pest_obs["id_geno_semis"])

print(data_pest_obs.shape)
data_pest_obs.head()

# =========================
# 6. Load and Prepare Survival Interval Data
# =========================
data_survival_int_range = pd.read_csv(
    "survival_int_range_py.csv", sep=";", index_col=0, decimal=","
)
data_survival_int_range = data_survival_int_range.sort_values(by="id_geno_semis")
survival_int_range_id = jnp.array(data_survival_int_range["id_geno_semis"])
survival_int_range_tt = jnp.array(
    data_survival_int_range[[f"{i}" for i in range(2, 101)]]
)

(pest_id == survival_int_range_id).all()
(data["sowing"][pest_id - 1][:, 1] == data_pest_obs["S2"]).all()
(data["sowing"][pest_id - 1][:, 0] == data_pest_obs["S1"]).all()

print(survival_int_range_tt.shape)
data_survival_int_range.head()
cov = jnp.array(
    [
        # jnp.zeros(shape=(len(data_pest_obs["attack.date.numeric"]),)),
        jnp.ones(shape=(len(data_pest_obs["attack.date.numeric"]),)),
        # data_pest_obs["S0"],
        data_pest_obs["S1"],
        data_pest_obs["S2"],
    ]
).T

# cov = jnp.array(
#     [
#         jnp.zeros(shape=(len(data_pest_obs["attack.date.numeric"]),)),
#         jnp.zeros(shape=(len(data_pest_obs["attack.date.numeric"]),)),
#         jnp.zeros(shape=(len(data_pest_obs["attack.date.numeric"]),)),
#     ]
# ).T
print(cov.shape)

data = data | {
    "T": jnp.array(data_pest_obs["attack.date.numeric"]),
    "id_t2y": pest_id - 1,
    "delta": ~jnp.isnan(jnp.array(data_pest_obs["attack.date.numeric"])),
    "cov": cov,
    "survival_int_range_tt": survival_int_range_tt,
}

data["T"] = jnp.where(data["delta"], data["T"], jnp.nanmax(data["T"]))
data["survival_int_range"] = jnp.linspace(0, data["T"], num=100)[1:].T
print(survival_int_range_tt.shape == data["survival_int_range"].shape)

# =========================
# 7. PolyMixedEffectsModel Fitting
# =========================

N, J = data["Y"].shape
mem = PolyMixedEffectsModel(N=N, J=J)

p_mem_start = mem.new_params(
    mean_latent={"mu0": 5.54e1, "mu2": 3.74e-3},
    mu2S=jnp.array([-1.93e-3, -3.7e-3]),
    mu1=jnp.array(-8.41e-02),
    mu3=jnp.array(-9.32e-5),
    cov_latent=jnp.diag(jnp.array([1.2, 0.001])) ** 2,
    var_residual=1.82,
)

if mode == "plotting":
    plot_digestibility(data, data_dig_obs)
    sdgplt.plt.savefig(f"digestibility{key}.png")

if mode in ["estimation", "jm and mem"]:
    algo_mem = algo_factory(mem, max_iter=2000, fisher_max=1)
    algo_mem.set_seed(jax_key)
    algo_mem.estimate_average_length = 1000
    res_mem = algo_mem.fit(
        mem,
        data,
        mem.parametrization.params_to_reals1d(p_mem_start),
    )
    res_mem.theta_star = p_mem_start

    res_mem.save(f"fit_mem")
    print(f"chrono: {res_mem.chrono}")

    fig = sdgplt.figure(8, 8)
    _ = sdgplt.plot_theta(
        res_mem,
        params_names=p_mem_names,
        id_to_plot=[[0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5], [6, 9] + [10]],
        fig=[*fig.subfigures(1, 2)],
        log_scale=False,
    )
    sdgplt.plt.savefig(f"fit_mem{key}.png")

    p_mem_hat = mem.new_params(
        mean_latent={
            "mu0": res_mem.last_theta[0],
            "mu2": res_mem.last_theta[1],
        },
        mu2S=res_mem.last_theta[2:4],
        mu1=res_mem.last_theta[4],
        mu3=res_mem.last_theta[5],
        cov_latent=jnp.diag(res_mem.last_theta[6:10:3]),
        var_residual=res_mem.last_theta[10],
    )
    print(f"p_mem = {p_mem_hat}")

if mode == "only_jm":
    p_mem_hat = mem.new_params(
        mean_latent={
            "mu0": 5.54e1,
            "mu2": 3.74e-3,
        },
        mu2S=jnp.array([-1.93e-3, -3.7e-3]),
        mu1=jnp.array(-8.41e-02),
        mu3=jnp.array(-9.32e-5),
        cov_latent=jnp.diag(jnp.array([1.66, 0.001])) ** 2,
        var_residual=1.82,
    )
    print(f"p_mem = {p_mem_hat}")

# =========================
# 8. Mixture Cox Model Fitting
# =========================
_, P = data["cov"].shape
(Nt,) = data["T"].shape
sm = MixtureCoxModel(N=Nt, P=P, nbr_mixture=2)
p_sm_start = sm.new_params(
    c=jnp.array([4.29163596, 12.92747718]),
    scale=jnp.array([60.1673112, 115.3815152]),
    pi=jnp.array([0.559]),
    beta=jnp.array([-2.04662442, 0.02829284, 0.69908498]),
)

if mode == "plotting":
    plot_T_hist_weibull(data, p_sm_start)
    sdgplt.plt.savefig(f"fit_survival_T_hist_weibull{key}.png")

if mode in ["only_sm", "estimation"]:
    algo_survival = algo_factory(
        sm,
        max_iter=4000,
        fisher_max=0.9,
        preheating=float(jnp.log(1e-4)),
        algo_type="PGD",
    )

    res_sm = algo_survival.fit(
        sm,
        data,
        sm.parametrization.params_to_reals1d(p_sm_start),
        freezed_components=jnp.array(
            # [False, False, False, False, False, True, True, False]
            [True, True, True, False, False, False, False, False]
        ),
    )
    res_sm.theta_star = p_sm_start
    res_sm.save(f"fit_survival")
    print(f"chrono: {res_sm.chrono}")

    _ = sdgplt.plot_theta(
        res_sm, params_names=p_surival_names, fig=sdgplt.figure(8, 8), log_scale=False
    )
    sdgplt.plt.savefig(f"fit_survival{key}.png")

    # =========================
    # 9. Plot Survival Model Fit
    # =========================

    p_sm_hat = sm.new_params(
        beta=res_sm.last_theta[:P],
        c=res_sm.last_theta[P : P + 2],
        scale=res_sm.last_theta[P + 2 : P + 4],
        pi=res_sm.last_theta[P + 4 : P + 5],
    )
    print(f"p_sm_hat = {p_sm_hat}")
    plot_T_hist_weibull(data, p_sm_hat)
    sdgplt.plt.savefig(f"fit_survival_T_hist_weibull{key}.png")

if mode == "only_jm":
    p_sm_hat = sm.new_params(
        beta=jnp.array([-2.04662442, 0.02829284, 0.69908498]),
        c=jnp.array([4.18130532, 12.84359147]),
        scale=jnp.array([60.49720925, 115.472039]),
        pi=jnp.array([0.56598768]),
    )
    p_sm_hat = sm.new_params(
        beta=jnp.array([-2.04662442, 0.02829284, 0.69908498]),
        c=jnp.array([3, 2]),
        scale=jnp.array([56, 80]),
        pi=jnp.array([0.25698768]),
    )
    plot_T_hist_weibull(data, p_sm_hat)
    sdgplt.plt.savefig(f"fit_survival_T_hist_weibull{key}.png")
    print(f"p_sm_hat = {p_sm_hat}")

# =========================
# 10. Joint Model Preparation
# =========================

JM = WeibullCoxMemJointModel(
    Nmem=mem.N, Ncox=sm.N, J=J, P=P, nbr_mixture=2, alpha_scale=1e-2
)

if mode in ["estimation", "only_jm", "jm and mem"]:
    p_JM_start = JM.new_params(
        mean_latent={
            "mu0": p_mem_hat.mean_latent.mu0,
            "mu2": p_mem_hat.mean_latent.mu2,
        },
        mu2S=p_mem_hat.mu2S,
        mu1=p_mem_hat.mu1,
        mu3=p_mem_hat.mu3,
        cov_latent=p_mem_hat.cov_latent,
        var_residual=p_mem_hat.var_residual,
        alpha=0.000,
        beta=p_sm_start.beta,
        c=p_sm_start.c,
        scale=p_sm_start.scale,
        pi=p_sm_start.pi,
    )
    algo_jm = algo_factory(
        JM,
        max_iter=10000,
        fisher_max=1,
        preheating=float(jnp.log(1e-8)),
        algo_type="SPG",
    )
    algo_jm.set_seed(jax_key)
    algo_jm._partial_fit = True
    algo_jm._pre_heating = 0

    res_jm = algo_jm.fit(
        JM,
        data,
        JM.parametrization.params_to_reals1d(p_JM_start),
        freezed_components=~jnp.array(
            [True, True, True, True, True, True]
            + [True, True]
            + [True]
            + [False]
            + [False, False, False]
            + [False, False, False, False, False]
        ),
    )

    fig = sdgplt.figure(16, 6 * 4)
    _ = sdgplt.plot_theta(
        res_jm,
        fig=[*fig.subfigures(1, 4)],
        params_names=p_jm_names,
        id_to_plot=[
            [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5],
            [6, 9] + [10, 11],
            [12 + i for i in range(3)],
            [15 + i for i in range(5)],
        ],
        log_scale=False,
    )
    sdgplt.plt.savefig(f"fit_joint_model{key}.png")

    algo_jm.skip_initialization = True
    res_jm += algo_jm.fit(
        JM,
        data,
        res_jm.last_theta_reals1d,
        freezed_components=~jnp.array(
            [False, False, False, False, False, False]
            + [False, False]
            + [False]
            + [False]
            + [False, False, False]
            + [True, True, True, True, True]
        ),
    )

    fig = sdgplt.figure(16, 6 * 4)
    _ = sdgplt.plot_theta(
        res_jm,
        fig=[*fig.subfigures(1, 4)],
        params_names=p_jm_names,
        id_to_plot=[
            [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5],
            [6, 9] + [10, 11],
            [12 + i for i in range(3)],
            [15 + i for i in range(5)],
        ],
        log_scale=False,
    )
    sdgplt.plt.savefig(f"fit_joint_model{key}.png")

    algo_jm.skip_initialization = True
    res_jm += algo_jm.fit(
        JM,
        data,
        res_jm.last_theta_reals1d,
        freezed_components=~jnp.array(
            [True, True, True, True, True, True]
            + [True, True]
            + [True]
            + [True]
            + [False, False, False]
            + [True, True, True, True, False]
        ),
    )

    res_jm.theta_star = p_JM_start
    res_jm.save(f"fit_joint_model{key}")
    print(f"chrono: {res_jm.chrono}")

    fig = sdgplt.figure(16, 6 * 4)
    _ = sdgplt.plot_theta(
        res_jm,
        fig=[*fig.subfigures(1, 4)],
        params_names=p_jm_names,
        id_to_plot=[
            [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5],
            [6, 9] + [10, 11],
            [12 + i for i in range(3)],
            [15 + i for i in range(5)],
        ],
        log_scale=False,
    )
    sdgplt.plt.savefig(f"fit_joint_model{key}.png")

    sdgplt.plot_mcmc(algo_jm)
    sdgplt.plt.savefig(f"mcmc{key}.png")
